Determine who the virtual event will be accessible to users
  • Open in new window will use the web client of the source (Zoom or BBB)
  • Open in source app will open the meeting in the desktop or mobile app of the source (Zoom is currently supported)
  • pen in modal, similar to open in new page but uses the modal (overlay) window using Drupal native modal
